data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful 2-story home located in the lovely Hidden River neighborhood. This delightful residence boasts 3 bedrooms, a loft, and 2 bathrooms. As you enter the home, you'll immediately notice the open living concept, creating a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The highlight of the living room is the large wood-burning fireplace. French doors in the living room lead to the back yard, allowing for easy access to outdoor entertainment and relaxation.
The kitchen features stainless-steel appliances and an abundance of natural light, creating an inviting space to prepare delicious meals and entertain guests. Heading upstairs, you'll discover 2 spacious bedrooms and a versatile loft area. The partially-finished basement adds even more living space to this already impressive home. It features a comfortable living room where you can gather with loved ones for movie nights or game days. The large back yard is a true oasis, complete with a large deck and a gazebo. This home is equipped with a range of smart home features. With a BHIVE sprinkler system, Nest thermostat, and a garage door opener, you can effortlessly control various aspects of your home. The Vivint Security System provides peace of mind with floodlights, backyard cameras, a front door lock, and a front door bell, along with an indoor camera. Situated within walking distance to parks and schools. Additionally, it is ideally located near shopping centers, restaurants, and entertainment options, allowing for easy access to all the amenities you desire.
